stories.text:
We have received funding to create a new startup that coordiates crisis-actors-as-service and would like to gauge interest in the community.

Corporate partners will be able to create private campaigns and users will be able to sign up for paid protest operations in their region. Actors will be paid market wages ($19-22.50/hr) and be thoroughly vetted using our proprietary algorithm to ensure our paid protest operations appear legitimate.

Would you be interested in using such a service to further your corporate interests? Let us know. Thank-you.
